                  </p>
                </div>

                <div
                  class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm mb-6"
                >
                  <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Book:</h4>
                  <p class="mb-4 pl-6 text-sm">
                    Author, A. A. (Year). <em>Title of book</em>. Publisher.
                  </p>
                  <p class="mb-2 font-bold">Example:</p>
                  <p class="pl-6 text-sm">
                    Wilson, J. (2021).
                    <em
                      >Supporting transitions to adulthood for youth with
                      special needs</em
                    >. Academic Press.
                  </p>
                </div>

                <div
                  class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm mb-6"
                >
                  <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Book Chapter:</h4>
                  <p class="mb-4 pl-6 text-sm">
                    Author, A. A., &amp; Author, B. B. (Year). Title of chapter.
                    In E. E. Editor &amp; F. F. Editor (Eds.),
                    <em>Title of book</em> (pp. page range). Publisher.
                  </p>
                  <p class="mb-2 font-bold">Example:</p>
                  <p class="pl-6 text-sm">
                    Patel, P., &amp; Thompson, A. (2023). Building inclusive
                    community spaces. In S. Johnson &amp; M. Chen (Eds.),
                    <em
                      >Community-based supports for youth with special needs</em
                    >
                    (pp. 45-67). Oxford University Press.
                  </p>
                </div>

                <div
                  class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm mb-6"
                >
                  <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Website:</h4>
                  <p class="mb-4 pl-6 text-sm">
                    Author, A. A. (Year, Month Day). <em>Title of page</em>.
                    Site Name. URL
                  </p>
                  <p class="mb-2 font-bold">Example:</p>
                  <p class="pl-6 text-sm">
                    Centers for Disease Control and Prevention. (2022, March
